title: United States 8 Week Bill Yield
description: US 8 Week Bill Bond Yield was 3.93 percent on Wednesday November 9, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United States 8 Week Bill Yield reached an all time high of 3.99 in November of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United States 8 Week Bill Yield.
author: Federal Reserve
